      "description": "This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, preserved in impeccable showroom condition. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, reflects a standard of care that is rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this unit offers an unparalleled driving experience for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
